Bikini Frankenstein is not scary at all. It is sexy and fast paced! Some of the campy humor works. I am a big fan of Brandin Rackley and Christine Nguyen. This soft core porn comedy is loosely based on the book Frankenstein. The CGI and production values are decent considering the low budget. The indoor footage was filmed in someone's house! This is the kind of soft core erotica that one finds on Cinemax late at night. Bikini Frankenstein is decent, sublime soft core porn.
Nudity or not the comedy was a big LOL.
Just like Vamps. I recommend this for all movie collectors.
